  'Group therapy DAP (Data, Assessment, Plan) notes organized by client engagement level',
  'Group Therapy DAP Note

Group Topic: [TOPIC]

Positive Clients

[Continue with Notes 2-5 following same D/A/P format]

[Continue with Notes 7-25 following same D/A/P format]

Note 26

A: [Assessment of client emotional state, progress, and concerns]
P: [Plan for continued support and therapeutic interventions]

[Continue with Notes 27-30 following same D/A/P format]',
  'false',
  1
)
